I"ƒ<p>Very simple. Register, sync your GitHub repo, commit and push.</p>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Sign in to <a href="https://travis-ci.org/">https://travis-ci.org/</a> with your Github account.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Go to <a href="https://travis-ci.org/profile/">https://travis-ci.org/profile/</a> and enable <em>username</em>/openclassifieds2.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Commit and push something to your <em>username</em>/openclassifieds2 repo. Go to <a href="https://travis-ci.org/">https://travis-ci.org/</a>, click on the repository on the left sidebar and select a job from the bottom of the main page to see the Job Log.</p>
  </li>
</ol>

